packets.name: E1337 Signature Gold T-shirt
packets.author: Voxel-Architect
packets.description: The first NFT wearable from E1337's Signature range, the E1337 Signature Gold T-shirt. Launching in 2020, E1337 is the world's first E-sports apparel brand that is designed and made in the E-sports Mecca, South Korea. This NFT wearable marks the first public announcement of E1337's launch at the WIP event held on June 25th 2020.
